s%2Fkartik-aaryans-bodyguard-manhandles-fans-amidst-frenzy-at-theatre-watch-actors-reaction%2Farticleshow%2F114933632.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20MPs%20Write%20To%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Over%20Waqf%20Bill%20Committee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20wrote%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20Monday%2C%20warning%20that%20they%20could%20'dissociate'%20themselves%20from%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20studying%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MPs%20accused%20the%20committee%20Chair%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20Jagadambika%20Pal%2C%20of%20taking%20decisions%20regarding%20meeting%20dates%20and%20summons%20for%20consultations%20-%20unilaterally%2C%20and%20called%20his%20actions%20a%20%26quot%3Bforceful%20way%20to%20mitigate%20(protests)%20and%20pass%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%26quot%3B.%20They%20said%20they%20would%20walk%20away%20if%20not%20given%20sufficient%20time%20to%20present%20concerns%20about%20changes%20to%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20were%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%20in%20August%20and%2C%20amid%20furious%20protests%20from%20opposition%20MPs%20(and%20questions%20from%20some%20key%20BJP%20allies)%20sent%20to%20the%20JPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20sittings%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20protests%20and%20walkouts%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20there%20was%20drama%20after%20Trinamool%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20smashed%20a%20glass%20bottle%20-%20while%20arguing%20with%20the%20BJP's%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20-%20and%20threw%20the%20remains%20at%20Mr%20Pal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20cut%20his%20fingers%2C%20later%20said%20his%20'Hulk'%20moment%20had%20been%20provoked%20by%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20a%20former%20Justice%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20verbally%20abusing%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20leader%20also%20accused%20the%20Chairperson%20-%20Jagadambika%20Pal%20-%20of%20favouring%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20his%20BJP%20colleague%2C%20declaring%20%26quot%3Bhe%20was%20harsh%20to%20me%20but%20soft%20to%20him%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20have%20also%20questioned%20the%20JPC%20hearing%20from%20groups%20-%20such%20as%20Odisha-based%20Panchasakha%20Bani%20Prachar%20-%20arguing%20that%20these%20have%20no%20stake%20in%20discussions%20on%20the%20Waqf%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20is%20scheduled%20to%20meet%20today%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20Delhi-based%20Jamaat-e-Islam-e-Hind%2C%20a%20Shia%20Muslim%20group%2C%20and%20the%20Jamiyat%20Himaytul%20Islam%20led%20by%20Qari%20Abrar%20Jamal.%20It%20will%20also%20hear%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20it%20began%20meeting%2C%20from%20a%20Muslim%20women's%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20the%20committee%20is%20expected%20to%20hear%20from%20the%20Akhil%20Bhartiya%20Adhivakta%20Parishad%2C%20which%20is%20an%20organisation%20of%20lawyers%20associated%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20which%20is%20the%20ruling%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20proposed%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20laws%20(apart%20from%20having%20non-Muslim%20members%20on%20the%20board)%20is%20a%20provision%20to%20include%20at%20least%20two%20women%2C%20including%20the%20Central%20Council.%20Sources%20have%20told%20NDTV%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20empower%20Muslim%20women%20and%20children%20who%20%26quot%3Bsuffered%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20old%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20three%20BJP%20allies%20-%20including%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20and%20his%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20Chandrababu%20Naidu's%20TDP%2C%20both%20of%20whom%20are%20critical%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20party%20maintaining%20its%20government%20-%20have%20also%20spoken%20out%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730704080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fbv2pgbe8_waqf-meet_625x300_14_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-jpc-opposition-mps-write-to-lok-sabha-speaker-over-waqf-bill-committee-6939661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20MPs%20wrote%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20Monday%2C%20warning%20that%20they%20could%20'dissociate'%20themselves%20from%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20studying%20changes%20to%20the%20Waqf%20Bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Pakistan%20can%20beat%20India%20%E2%80%A6'%3A%20Wasim%20Akram's%20big%20statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730703784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114936882%2Cimgsize-48484.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fpakistan-can-beat-india-wasim-akrams-big-statement-after-indias-historic-series-loss-against-new-zealand%2Farticleshow%2F114936724.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20India's%200-3%20series%20loss%20to%20New%20Zealand%20at%20home%2C%20Michael%20Vaughan%20and%20Wasim%20Akram%20suggested%20a%20Test%20series%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20noting%20the%20potential%20excitement.%20Vaughan%20believes%20Pakistan%20can%20beat%20India%20on%20spin-friendly%20pitches%2C%20supported%20by%20their%20recent%20series%20win%20against%20England.%20Fans%20and%20experts%20are%20eagerly%20discussing%20this%20possibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Top%20Cop%20Transferred%20After%20Opposition's%20Phone%20Tapping%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20before%20Maharashtra%20votes%20in%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20ordered%20the%20transfer%20of%20Maharashtra%20DGP%20Rashmi%20Shukla%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20was%20biased%20towards%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20and%20that%20fair%20polls%20wouldn't%20be%20possible%20if%20she%20was%20in%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poll%20body%20has%20asked%20Chief%20Secretary%20Sujata%20Saunik%20to%20hand%20over%20Ms%20Shukla's%20charge%20to%20the%20next%20seniormost%20IPS%20officer%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20send%20a%20panel%20of%20three%20names%20by%20tomorrow%20for%20selection%20of%20the%20next%20state%20police%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20review%20meetings%20and%20announcement%20of%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20had%20warned%20officials%20to%20be%20impartial%20and%20fair%20and%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20perceived%20as%20non-partisan%20in%20conducting%20their%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20had%20accused%20Ms%20Shukla%20of%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20allegation%20against%20the%20state's%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Rashmi%20Shukla.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20our%20government%20was%20being%20formed%2C%20this%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20who%20was%20directly%20working%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20was%20tapping%20all%20our%20phones%20and%20giving%20full%20information%20to%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20about%20what%20we%20were%20going%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanjay%20Raut%2C%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%2C%20had%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20we%20expect%20her%20to%20conduct%20fair%20elections%3F%20We%20have%20said%20that%20the%20reins%20of%20elections%20should%20not%20be%20given%20to%20her%2C%20and%20then%20the%20Election%20Commission%20said%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20right%20(to%20transfer).%20How%20can%20this%20happen%3F%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Jharkhand's%20DGP%20was%20changed.%20Maharashtra's%20election%20is%20being%20conducted%20based%20on%20police%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20chief%20Nana%20Patole%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20requesting%20Ms%20Shukla's%20removal%20from%20the%20post%20of%20the%20state%20police%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patole%20had%20accused%20the%20senior%20woman%20police%20officer%20of%20displaying%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20bias%26quot%3B%20against%20Opposition%20parties.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%2020%20days%2C%20political%20violence%20against%20opposition%20parties%20has%20significantly%20escalated%2C%20with%20a%20notable%20deterioration%20in%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20She%20has%20shown%20a%20clear%20bias%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20and%20NCP(SP)%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20her%20previous%20record%20of%20illegal%20phone%20tapping%20of%20opposition%20leaders%20while%20serving%20as%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20State%20Intelligence%20Department%20(SID)%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%2C%20has%20welcomed%20the%20top%20cop's%20transfer.%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt%20became%20clear%20today%20that%20the%20coalition%20government%20was%20being%20dishonest.%20What%20was%20the%20compulsion%20of%20the%20alliance%20government%20to%20extend%20the%20term%20of%20police%20officer%20Rashmi%20Shukla%20who%20was%20facing%20serious%20charges%3F%20She%20was%20given%20an%20extension%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20not%20conducted%20in%20a%20transparent%2