0Conference%2C%20said%20he%20had%20not%20yet%20admitted%20any%20such%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20-%20who%20earlier%20said%20it%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfoolish%26quot%3B%20to%20expect%20the%20BJP%20to%20restore%20Article%20370%20-%20said%20he%20knew%20a%20resolution%20to%20this%20effect%20was%20coming%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20do%20not%20approve%20of%20the%20decision%20taken%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%20If%20they%20had%20approved%2C%20then%20the%20results%20today%20would%20have%20been%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20the%20House%20will%20reflect%20and%20discuss%20this%20will%20not%20be%20decided%20by%20any%20one%20member.%20The%20resolution%20brought%20today%20has%20no%20importance%20but%20it%20is%20only%20for%20the%20cameras.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20purpose%20behind%20it%2C%20then%20they%20would%20have%20discussed%20this%20with%20us%20before...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20centre%20revoked%20Article%20370%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20a%20contentious%20move%20marked%20by%20furious%20protests%20from%20political%20parties%20and%20politicians%20in%20Jammu%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley.%20The%20revocation%20was%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%2C%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farticle-370-verdict-live-updates-supreme-court-verdict-on-validity-of-scrapping-article-370-in-jammu-and-kashmir-today-4652207%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruled%20the%20provision%20a%20%26quot%3Btemporary%26quot%3B%20one%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%20had%20given%20J%26amp%3BK%20special%20status%20and%20privileges.%20Post%20its%20removal%20the%20central%20government%20also%20split%20the%20former%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories%20-%20that%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%2C%20separately%2C%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestoration%20of%2