ed%20not%20to%20field%20any%20candidate%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Maratha%20community%20will%20decide%20on%20its%20own%20whom%20to%20defeat%20and%20whom%20to%20elect.%20I%20have%20no%20affiliation%20to%20or%20support%20for%20any%20candidate%20or%20political%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20under%20no%20pressure%20from%20anyone.%20The%20community%20itself%20will%20decide%20whom%20to%20support%20based%20on%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20Maratha%20cause%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20wronged%20or%20harassed%20the%20Maratha%20community%20should%20be%20taught%20a%20lesson%20through%20the%20ballot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20contest%20and%20win%20an%20election%20on%20the%20strength%20of%20one%20caste.%20We%20are%20new%20in%20politics.%20If%20we%20field%20a%20candidate%20and%20he%20loses%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20shame%20for%20the%20caste.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20request%20all%20the%20Maratha%20candidates%20to%20withdraw%20their%20nomination%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20activist%2C%20who%20made%20national%20headlines%20during%20his%20hunger%20strike%20demanding%20reservation%20benefits%20for%20Marathas%2C%20had%20earlier%20said%20he%20would%20support%20candidates%20challenging%20MLAs%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region.%20This%20region%20includes%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%2C%20Beed%2C%20Hingoli%2C%20Jalna%2C%20Latur%2C%20Nanded%2C%20Osmanabad%20and%20Parbhani%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%20Jarange-Patil's%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20election%20is%20likely%20to%20benefit%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20as%20it%20would%20prevent%20the%20division%20of%20anti-BJP%20votes.%20Maratha%20votes%20were%20widely%20seen%20as%20a%20key%20factor%20behind%20the%20NDA's%20poor%20show%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20the%20general%20election%20earlier%20this%20year.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20activist%20had%20targeted%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%2C%20specifically%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20(Eknath%20Shinde)%20had%20promised%20to%20provide%20us%20the%20reservation.%20We%20pinned%20hopes%20on%20him.%20But%20Fadnavis%20did%20not%20let%20that%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFadnavis%20made%20the%20game%20plan.%20He%20told%20the%20Centre%20how%20the%20party%20will%20benefit%20through%20the%20OBCs%20by%20denying%20reservation%20to%20the%20Marathas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20activist%20had%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Shinde%20had%20said%20Manoj%20Jarange-Patil%20should%20look%20at%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20in%20the%20Marathas'%20interest.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Dussehra%20rally%2C%20I%20touched%20the%20feet%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj's%20statue%20and%20took%20an%20oath...%20After%20that%20I%20immediately%20called%20a%20session%20of%20the%20state%20legislature%20and%20gave%20the%20Maratha%20community%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation.%20But%20this%20issue%20went%20to%20court...%20Before%20this%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20had%20given%20reservation%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20However%2C%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20could%20not%20ensure%20that%20it%20is%20upheld%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJarange%20has%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20But%20he%20should%20first%20ponder%20over%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20Mahayuti%20Government%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Maratha%20community.%20Now%20the%20Maratha%20community%20is%20getting%20benefits%20like%20OBCs.%20Who%20did%20all%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publis