%20efforts%20by%20anti%20India%20elements%2C%20our%20Consulate%20was%20able%20to%20issue%20more%20than%201000%20life%20certificates%20to%20the%20Indian%20and%20Canadian%20applicants.%20There%20were%20also%20attempts%20to%20disrupt%20similar%20camps%20held%20in%20Vancouver%20and%20Surrey%20on%20Nov%202-3%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20in%20light%20of%20these%20incidents%20and%20with%20Indian%20diplomats%20receiving%20threats%2C%20the%20organisation%20of%20more%20scheduled%20consular%20camps%20would%20depend%20on%20security%20arrangements%20by%20local%20authorities%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20case%20any%20camp%20is%20infeasible%20to%20be%20held%20due%20to%20such%20disruptions%2C%20alternative%20arrangements%20will%20be%20made%20to%20render%20those%20services%2C%20which%20may%20unfortunately%20inconvenience%20local%20users%20of%20these%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Commission%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Indian-Canadian%20leaders%2C%20including%20MP%20Chandra%20Arya%2C%20have%20alleged%20that%20Khalistani%20extremists%20were%20behind%20the%20violence%20at%20the%20Hindu%20Sabha%20Mandir%20temple.%20Some%20videos%20that%20went%20viral%20show%20a%20group%20of%20men%20attacking%20devotees%20at%20the%20temple.%C2%A0A%20spokesperson%20for%20Peel%20Regional%20Police%20told%20AFP%20that%20no%20arrests%20had%20been%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Arya%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bred%20line%20has%20been%20crossed%20by%20Canadian%20Khalistani%20extremists%20today%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20attack%20by%20Khalistanis%20on%20the%20Hindu-Canadian%20devotees%20inside%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Sabha%20temple%20in%20Brampton%20shows%20how%20deep%20and%20brazen%20Khalistani%20violent%20extremism%20has%20become%20in%20Canada.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20responded%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20temple%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bunacceptable%26quot