%20A%20Radical%20Shift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20has%20admitted%20to%20being%20a%20Democrat%20prior%20to%20the%202016%20elections.%20His%20political%20worldview%20shifted%20dramatically%20during%20this%20time%2C%20particularly%20in%20response%20to%20Mr%20Trump's%20rise.%20In%20various%20tweets%2C%20The%20SpaceX%20chief%20has%20expressed%20disillusionment%20with%20established%20political%20norms%20and%20what%20he%20perceives%20as%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20political%20elite%20to%20address%20the%20real%20needs%20of%20the%20American%20people.%20The%20divisive%20atmosphere%20of%20the%202016%20election%20seems%20to%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20reshaping%20his%20beliefs%2C%20leading%20him%20to%20embrace%20a%20more%20libertarian%20ethos%20that%20pushes%20for%20individual%20freedom%20and%20scepticism%20of%20government%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mr%20Trump%20assumed%20the%20presidency%2C%20Mr%20Musk's%20political%20donations%20began%20to%20skew%20significantly%20Republican.%20By%202017%2C%20he%20was%20reportedly%20spending%20nearly%20seven%20times%20more%20on%20GOP%20campaigns%20than%20Democratic%20ones.%20His%20willingness%20to%20accept%20positions%20on%20two%20of%20Mr%20Trump's%20White%20House%20councils%20highlighted%20a%20shift%20in%20stance.%20While%20Mr%20Musk%20initially%20backed%20Hillary%20Clinton's%20environmental%20platform%2C%20he%20justified%20his%20participation%20in%20Mr%20Trump's%20business%20council%20as%20a%20means%20to%20raise%20critical%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20controversial%20travel%20ban%20targeting%20Muslim-majority%20countries.%20However%2C%20he%20resigned%20from%20these%20councils%20in%20June%202017%2C%20citing%20Mr%20Trump's%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20Paris%20Climate%20Accord%2C%20tweeting%2C%20%26quot%3BClimate%20change%20is%20real.%20Leaving%20Paris%20is%20not%20good%20for%20America%20or%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Bre