Cp%3EMr%20Zuckerburg%20has%20hired%20prominent%20Republican%20strategist%20Brian%20Baker%20to%20help%20repair%20Meta's%20strained%20relationship%20with%20conservative%20media%20and%20officials.%20The%202020%20%26quot%3BZuckerbucks%26quot%3B%20controversy%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20become%20a%20flashpoint%20in%20Republican%20criticism%20of%20the%20Meta%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zuckerberg%20has%20also%20pivoted%20away%20from%20the%20political%20discourse%20that%20characterised%20his%20company's%20approach%20during%20the%202020%20presidential%20polls.%20Just%20days%20before%20that%20election%2C%20Mr%20Zuckerberg%20was%20concerned%20about%20potential%20civil%20unrest%20resulting%20from%20a%20divided%20nation.%20He%20stated%20that%20Meta%20needed%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Bwell%20beyond%20what%20we've%20done%20before%26quot%3B%20to%20protect%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20statement%20announcing%20lacklustre%20third-quarter%20results%2C%20Mr%20Zuckerberg%20omitted%20any%20mention%20of%20democracy%20or%20election%20integrity.%20Instead%2C%20he%20expressed%20a%20focus%20on%20creating%20innovative%20products%2C%20leading%20analysts%20to%20question%20Meta's%20commitment%20to%20political%20accountability.%20This%20abrupt%20change%20is%20especially%20striking%20for%20those%20who%20recall%20Mr%20Zuckerberg's%20frequent%20reassurances%20about%20safeguarding%20the%20electoral%20process%20and%20combating%20misinformation%20during%20key%20electoral%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Silicon%20Valley%20Votes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20once%20a%20liberal%20stronghold%2C%20tech%20elites%20are%20increasingly%20expressing%20support%20for%20Mr%20Trump.%20In%202016%2C%20nearly%20all%20political%20contributions%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20went%20to%20Hillary%20Clinton.%20By%202020%2C%20tech%20executives%20intensified%20their%20efforts%20to%20defeat%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20except%20for%20a%20handful%20of%20contrarians.%20But%20something%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20reported%20by%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20pledged%20%2445%20million%20per%20month%20to%20a%20pro-Trump%20super%20Political%20Action%20Committee%20(PAC)%20starting%20in%20July.%20%C2%A0Other%20tech%20heavyweights%20like%20David%20Sacks%2C%20a%20former%20critic%20of%20Mr%20Trump's%20actions%20surrounding%20the%20January%206%20Capitol%20riot%2C%20have%20also%20thrown%20their%20weight%20behind%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F5jp369v8_jeff-bezos_625x300_03_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Silicon%20Valley's%20heartlands%20of%20San%20Mateo%20and%20Santa%20Clara%20counties%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20voters%20remain%20registered%20Democrats%20as%20of%202022%2C%20with%20Republicans%20making%20up%20just%2015%20per%20cent.%20Historically%2C%20venture%20capitalists%20and%20tech%20executives%20overwhelmingly%20supported%20Democratic%20candidates.%20According%20to%20a%20Wired%20analysis%2C%20Democrats%20received%20%242%20for%20every%20dollar%20sent%20to%20Republicans%20from%20the%2020%20most%20active%20political%20contributors%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%20This%20remains%20consistent%20with%20a%202017%20study%20showing%20tech%20elites%20favouring%20progressive%20policies%2C%20from%20wealth%20redistribution%20to%20immigration%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20one%20key%20issue%20where%20tech%20moguls%20diverge%20from%20the%20Democratic%20platform%20-%20government%20regulation.%20As%20Biden%20ramps%20up%20antitrust%20lawsuits%20against%20major%20tech%20companies%2C%20including%20Apple%2C%20Alphabet%20(Google's%20parent)%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Amazon%2C%20some%20Silicon%20Valley%20elites%20are%20gravitating%20toward%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20whose%20economic%20stance%20and%20promises%20of%20lighter%20regulatory%20burdens%20appear%20more%20appealing%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration's%20crackdown%20on%20crypto%2C%20including%20lawsuits%20against%20Coinbase%20and%20Binance%2C%20has%20also%20nudged%20crypto%20moguls%20toward%20the%20Republican%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmazon%20chief%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20who%20has%20kept%20a%20more%20subdued%20profile%2C%20faced%20his%20own%20controversy%20when%20he%20abruptly%20cancelled%20The%20Washington%20Post's%20endorsement%20of%20Democratic%20nominee%20Kamala%20Harris%20-%20a%20decision%20that%20prompted%20a%20mass%20cancellation%20by%20Post%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20repercussions%20of%20Mr%20Bezos's%20decision%20were%20immediate%3A%20nearly%20a%20quarter-million%20Post%20readers%20ended%20their%20subscriptions%2C%20perceiving%20the%20move%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20appease%20Mr%20Trump.%20While%20Mr%20Bezos%20denies%20any%20political%20intent%2C%20many%20of%20The%20Post's%20loyal%20readers%20have%20their%20doubts%2C%20especially%20as%20it%20has%20often%20been%20critical%20of%20Mr%20Trump's%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20co-founder%20of%20ChatGPT's%20parent%20company%20Open%20AI%2C%20has%20consistently%20donated%20to%20Democrat%20politicians%20since%202013%2C%20as%20per%20data%20from%20OpenSecrets.%20Mr%20Altman%20has%20reportedly%20donated%20over%20%241%20million%20to%20Democratic%20candidates%20in%20his%20home%20state%20California%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2024%3A%20What's%20The%20Endgame%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20has%20used%20X%20to%20promote%20conservative%20causes%2C%20and%20push%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20often%20targeting%20immigration%20policies%20and%20railing%20against%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bwoke%20mind%20virus.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20his%20endorsement%20of%20Mr%20Trump%20and%20participation%20in%20his%20public%20rallies%20signals%20Mr%20Musk's%20deeper%20engagement%20in%20US%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElection%20officials%20in%20critical%20battleground%20states%20such%20as%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20Arizona%20are%20grappling%20with%20a%20surge%20in%20election%20misinformation%20emanating%20from%20X.%20Mr%20Musk's%20amplification%20of%20debunked%20election%20claims%20is%20posing%20a%20serious%20challenge%20for%20officials%20trying%20to%20maintain%20public%20trust%20in%20the%20voting%20process.%20Despite%20multiple%20attempts%20to%20fact-check%20Mr%20Musk%20in%20real%20time%2C%20election%20officials%20find%20themselves%20repeatedly%20outmatched.%20According%20to%20CNN%2C%20Stephen%20Richer%2C%20an%20Arizona%20election%20official%2C%20has%20even%20sent%20personal%20notes%20to%20Mr%20Musk%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20curb%20the%20spread%20of%20falsehoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichigan%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Jocelyn%20Benson%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20few%20officials%20able%20to%20counter%20Mr%20Musk's%20claims%20on%20X%20effectively.%20After%20Mr%20Musk%20posted%20inaccurate%20claims%20about%20Michigan's%20voter%20registration%2C%20Ms%20Benson's%20fact-check%20reached%20over%2033%20million%20views.%20But%20even%20this%20effort%20led%20Mr%20Musk%20to%20retaliate%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20lying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fvqgg5uk8_elon-musk-donald-trump-afp_625x300_04_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20battleground%20states%20like%20Georgia%2C%20officials%20are%20forgoing%20attempts%20to%20engage%20with%20Mr%20Musk%20directly%2C%20instead%20holding%20regular%20press%20conferences%20to%20counter%20misinformation.%20As%20the%20election%20nears%2C%20officials%20are%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20the%20unchecked%20spread%20of%20falsehoods%20on%20X%2C%20which%20they%20fear%20could%20lead%20to%20voter%20confusion%20and%20legal%20challenges%20post-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20misinformation%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20turning%20X%20into%20an%20echo%20chamber%20for%20conservative%20voices%2C%20reinstating%20White%20supremacists%20and%20conspiracy%20theorists%20while%20clamping%20down%20on%20content%20that%20challenges%20right-wing%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk's%20endorsement%20of%20Mr%20Trump%20goes%20beyond%20shared%20political%20ideologies.%20His%20vast%20business%20empire%20-%20spanning%20Tesla%2C%20SpaceX%2C%20Neuralink%2C%20and%20X-relies%20heavily%20on%20government%20contracts%2C%20subsidies%2C%20and%20favourable%20policies.%20Should%20Mr%20Trump%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20the%20tech%20billionaire%20stands%20to%20gain%20access%20to%20even%20more%20significant%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%20is%20building%20what%20he%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20largest%20supercomputer%26quot%3B%20in%20Memphis%20for%20his%20AI%20startup%2C%20xAI.%20This%20high-stakes%20project%2C%20however%2C%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20and%20concerns%20over%20its%20secrecy%20and%20potential%20impacts%20on%20local%20resources.%20According%20to%20a%20Forbes%20report%2C%20neither%20Memphis%20residents%20nor%20city%20council%20members%20were%20informed%20until%20the%20project%20was%20well%20underway%2C%20despite%20xAI's%20rapid%20progress%20and%20heavy%20resource%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20claims%20that%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20Mr%20Musk's%20representatives%20held%20confidential%20meetings%20with%20local%20and%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20FBI%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%2C%20and%20the%20Memphis%20Police%20Department.%20Organised%20by%20the%20Greater%20Memphis%20Chamber%2C%20the%20discussions%20around%20the%20project%20required%20attendees%20to%20sign%20non-disclosure%20agreements%20(NDAs)%20with%20CTC%20Property%2C%20a%20shell%20company%20managed%20by%20Mr%20Musk's%20close%20advisor%20Jared%20Birchall.%20Known%20for%20overseeing%20Mr%20Musk's%20ventures%20from%20SpaceX%20to%20Neuralink%2C%20Mr%20Birchall%20has%20reportedly%20enforced%20similar%20confidentiality%20on%20other%20Musk-led%20projects%20across%20the%20US%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20four%20months%2C%20xAI's%20Memphis%20facility%20-%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BColossus%26quot%3B%20-%20went%20online%20in%20a%20repurposed%20factory%20near%20the%20Mississippi%20River.%20This%20massive%20supercomputer%20will%20draw%20enough%20power%20for%20100%2C000%20homes%20and%20requires%20more%20than%20a%20million%20gallons%20of%20water%20daily%20for%20cooling.%20The%20Tennessee%20Valley%20Authority%20(TVA)%2C%20which%20will%20provide%20up%20to%20150%20megawatts%20of%20electricity%2C%20is%20now%20developing%20an%20entirely%20new%20substation%20to%20meet%20xAI's%20needs.%20TVA%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20its%20agreements%20with%20xAI%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20unclear%20if%20it%20signed%20an%20NDA%20with%20Mr%20Musk's%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handling%20of%20Mr%20Musk's%20project%20adds%20to%20the%20growing%20list%20of%20NDAs%20shielding%20corporate%20projects%20from%20public%20scrutiny.%20According%20to%20Forbes%2C%20in%20Texas%20and%20Nevada%2C%20Mr%20Musk's%20companies%20used%20similar%20agreements%20to%20conceal%20key%20details%20from%20state%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fo96vo4ag_elon-musk-donald-trump-afp-_625x300_04_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20AFP%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20element%20of%20Mr%20Musk's%20potential%20influence%20under%20a%20Trump%20presidency%20is%20the%20proposal%20that%20he%20lead%20a%20government%20efficiency%20commission.%20During%20their%20August%20conversation%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20suggested%20the%20creation%20of%20such%20a%20commission%20to%20rein%20in%20government%20spending%2C%20offering%20his%20expertise%20in%20cost-cutting.%20Mr%20Trump%20responded%20enthusiastically%2C%20praising%20the%20Tesla%20chief%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreatest%20cutter%26quot%3B%20of%20jobs%20and%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20call%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20commission%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20made.%20Former%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%20established%20a%20similar%20body%20called%20the%20Grace%20Commission%20during%20his%20presidency%20between%201981-89.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Mr%20Musk%20were%20to%20head%20such%20a%20commission%2C%20he%20would%20gain%20a%20direct%20role%20in%20shaping%20federal%20spending%20priorities%2C%20giving%20him%20unprecedented%20influence%20over%20the%20government's%20financial%20policies.%20This%20would%20also%20put%20him%20in%20a%20position%20to%20shape%20regulations%20that%20could%20benefit%20his%20own%20companies.%20SpaceX%2C%20for%20example%2C%20depends%20on%20federal%20contracts%20for%20rocket%20launches%2C%20while%20Tesla%20benefits%20from%20tax%20credits%20and%20subsidies%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20Mr%20Musk's%20involvement%20in%20government%20could%20give%20him%20the%20power%20to%20shape%20rules%20in%20ways%20that%20favour%20his%20business%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20SpaceX%20and%20Tesla%20have%20secured%20at%20least%20%2415%20billion%20in%20government%20contracts%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk's%20foray%20into%20national%20politics%20is%20not%20entirely%20unexpected.%20His%20personal%20and%20business%20ethos%20have%20always%20been%20aligned%20with%20a%20libertarian%2C