20takes%20a%20brilliant%20catch%2C%20you%20get%20a%20great%20delivery.%20I%20won't%20read%20too%20much%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fsunil-gavaskar-exclusive-interview-india-vs-new-zealand-9651679%2F%5C%22%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20top%20Indian%20batters%20should%20have%20played%20the%20Duleep%20Trophy%20ahead%20of%20the%20New%20Zealand%20series%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20match%20practice%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20Team%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20have%20had%20some%20practice%2C%20definitely.%20It's%20a%20long%20gap.%20I%20know%20we%20beat%20Bangladesh%20and%20therefore%20it%20looked%20as%20if%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20cakewalk%20against%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20New%20Zealand%20obviously%20had%20the%20better%20attack.%20And%20players%20who%20play%20in%20India%2C%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20what%20Indian%20pitches%20do.%20Almost%20half%20the%20New%20Zealand%20side%20played%20here%20during%20various%20stages%20of%20the%20IPL.%20So%2C%20they%20have%20an%20idea%20of%20what%20the%20pitches%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Test%20stars%20now%20have%20a%20few%20days%20off%20before%20they%20start%20prepreations%20for%20the%20Australia%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730687220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frgpq75h8_csa_625x300_03_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskar-delivers-clear-verdict-on-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-even-best-of-players-6935914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20believes%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20are%20going%20through%20a%20bad%20patch%20of%20form%20but%20added%20that%20people%20should%20not%20%26quot%3Bread%20too%20much%20into%20it%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A87%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Fsunil-gavaskar-delivers-clear-verdict-on-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-even-best-of-players-6935914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gambhir's%20Wings%20To%20Be%20Clipped%3F%20BCCI's%20'Big%20Step'%20After%20Poor%20Start%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnprecedented%20series%20defeats%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20New%20Zealand%20have%20placed%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20under%20immense%20pressure%20barely%20three%20months%20into%20his%20appointment%20as%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20team.%20He%20was%20appointed%20to%20the%20top%20post%20amid%20much%20fanfare%20and%20was%20also%20given%20a%20rare%20seat%20at%20the%20selection%20committee%20meeting%20for%20the%20tour%20of%20Australia.%20However%2C%20his%20initial%20report%20card%20clearly%20suggests%20things%20aren't%20looking%20good%20for%20the%20former%20India%20opener.%20Unless%20there%20is%20a%20remarkable%20turnaround%20Down%20Under%2C%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20was%20given%20a%20free%20hand%20in%20selection%20matters%2C%20may%20not%20have%20as%20much%20say%20in%20issues%20concerning%20the%20team%20in%20the%20coming%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERight%20after%20Gambhir%20took%20over%20the%20reins%2C%20India%20lost%20an%20ODI%20series%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2027%20years%2C%20and%20then%20New%20Zealand%20completed%20a%203-0%20whitewash%20of%20his%20side%20in%20Tests%20at%20home%20on%20Sunday%2C%20something%20the%20team%20never%20experienced%20in%20its%20long%20cricketing%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20coach%20can%20do%20only%20as%20much%2C%20questions%20are%20now%20being%20raised%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20prudence%20on%20display%20by%20going%20for%20a%20rank%20turner%20in%20Mumbai%20despite%20knowing%20that%20the%20top-order%20has%20time%20and%20again%20failed%20in%20last%20six%20to%20seven%20years%20against%20quality%20spin%20bowling%20on%20wickets%20offering%20decent%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Gambhir's%20philosophy%20of%20playing%20the%20same%20way%2C%20come%20hell%20or%20high%20water%2C%20is%20something%20that%20those%20associated%20closely%20with%20Indian%20cricket%20have%20failed%20to%20fathom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreeing%20to%20send%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20as%20night-watchman%20on%20the%20second%20evening%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20at%20No.8%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20are%20some%20of%20the%20tactical%20moves%20that%20are%20being%20questioned%20by%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGautam%20Gambhir%20was%20given%20access%20which%20his%20predecessors%20Ravi%20Shastri%20and%20Rahul%20Dravid%20didn't%20have.%20The%20BCCI's%20rule%20book%20doesn't%20allow%20coaches%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20meetings%2C%20but%20for%20Australia%20tour%20selection%20meeting%2C%20an%20exception%20was%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20head%20coach%20was%20allowed%20to%20attend%20considering%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20tour%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20BCCI%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20players%20--%20Delhi%20and%20KKR%20speedster%20Harshit%20Rana%20and%20Andhra%20and%20SRH%20all-rounder%20Nitish%20Reddy%20--%20are%20in%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20(BGT)%20squad%20on%20the%20insistence%20of%20the%20head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rana%20wasn't%20given%20any%20white-ball%20game%20in%20either%20Sri%20Lanka%20or%20during%20the%20home%20series%20against%20Bangladesh.%20It%20was%20reported%20that%20he%20was%20released%20before%20the%20last%20match%20as%20he%20was%20unwell%20but%20within%20a%20week%2C%20he%20was%20back%20bowling%20in%20the%20India%20nets%20in%20Bengaluru.%20And%20then%2C%20he%20had%20a%20good%20Ranji%20Trophy%20outing%20against%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20school%20of%20thought%20that%20believed%20Rana%2C%20rather%20than%20featuring%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20could%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20Australia%20with%20the%20India%20A%20team%20as%20playing%20one%20or%20two%20first-class%20games%20on%20bouncy%20tracks%20there%20would%20have%20allowed%20him%20to%20hit%20the%20right%20length%20before%20the%20Test%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20net%20bowler%20for%20the%20just-concluded%20Test%20series%20in%20which%20two%20of%20the%20three%20tracks%20were%20rank%20turners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20Reddy%2C%20he%20got%20into%20a%20tangle%20while%20facing%20a%20short%20ball%20in%20the%20'A'%20game%20and%20his%20bowling%2C%20which%20is%20certainly%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20be%20among%20the%20main%20five%20bowlers%2C%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImpressed%20with%20Reddy's%20T20%20skills%2C%20Gambhir%20was%20convinced%20that%20he%20can%20be%20the%20ideal%20replacement%20of%20Hardik%20Pandya%20as%20the%20seam%20bowling%20all-rounder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Australia%20series%20will%20be%20an%20acid%20test%20for%20Gambhir%20as%20he%20might%20have%20to%20also%20become%20the%20harbinger%20of%20doom%20for%20some%20senior%20players%20and%20show%20them%20the%20mirror%20as%20the%20board%20watches%20his%20moves%20from%20the%20sidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whitewash%20has%20also%20put%20the%20maverick%20Delhi%20man%20under%20the%20lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730687100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F7aceln6o_acs_625x300_03_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-new-zealand-2024%2Fbcci-to-take-big-step-on-gautam-gambhirs-sele