n%20and%20said%20the%20country's%20borders%20were%20safe%20till%20he%20was%20at%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20the%20safest%20border%20in%20the%20history%20of%20our%20country%20the%20day%20that%20I%20left.%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20left.%20I%20mean%2C%20honestly%2C%20because...%20we%20did%20so%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20President%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Lititz%2C%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20refused%20to%20concede%20the%202020%20election%20and%20unsuccessfully%20filed%20a%20series%20of%20court%20cases%20in%20challenging%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20rally%2C%20Trump%20also%20targeted%20Harris%20and%20accused%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bcorrupt%20machine%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20corrupt.%20She%20is%20corrupt.%20She%20is%20a%20corrupt%20person.%20I%20am%20running%20against%20a%20totally%20corrupt%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20really%20not%20running%20against%20her.%20I%20am%20running%20against%20a%20corrupt%20machine%20called%20the%20Democrat%20Party.%26quot%3B%20Pennsylvania%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20most%20crucial%20of%20the%20seven%20battleground%20states%20having%2019%20electoral%20college%20votes%20followed%20by%2016%20each%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%20Georgia%2C%2015%20in%20Michigan%20and%2011%20in%20Arizona.%20In%20other%20battleground%20states%2C%20Wisconsin%20has%2010%20and%20Nevada%20has%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20rally%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20Trump%20promised%20to%20usher%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20new%20golden%20age%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%20if%20he%20becomes%20the%20president%20and%20that%20he%20will%20%26quot%3Bfix%20the%20misdeeds%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20is%20also%20holding%20rallies%20in%20North%20Carolina%20and%20Georgia%20while%20Harris%20is%20touring%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20add