%20of%20political%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%2C%20also%20said%20the%20results%20bode%20well%20for%20Harris%20in%20other%20states.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20probably%20good%20news%20for%20Harris%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20Michigan%2C%20and%20elsewhere.%20If%20Harris%20is%20competitive%20in%20Iowa%2C%20combined%20with%20recent%20polling%20showing%20Trump%20with%20single-digit%20leads%20in%20Kansas%20and%20other%20red%20places%2C%20it%20bodes%20well%20for%20Harris.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20poll%2C%20so%20normally%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20read%20too%20much%20into%20one%20poll%2C%20but%20this%20is%20a%20pollster%20who's%20pretty%20good%20and%20has%20been%20working%20in%20Iowa%20for%20a%20long%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pollster%20%E2%80%94%20J.%20Ann%20Selzer%20%E2%80%94%20has%20had%20particular%20success%20predicting%20the%20Iowa%20caucuses%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelzer%20founded%20Selzer%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20in%201996.%20She%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffivethirtyeight.com%2Ffeatures%2Fselzer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econducts%20polling%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20private%20companies%20and%20public%20opinion%20surveys%20but%20Iowa%20politics%20remains%20her%20greatest%20strength%2C%20FiveThirtyEight%20reported%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Selzer%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatricia%20Crouse%2C%20adjunct%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20New%20Haven%2C%20said%20the%20Iowa%20poll%20is%20just%20one%20data%20point%20that%20shouldn't%20be%20used%20to%20predict%20the%20actual%20outcome%2C%20but%20that%20it's%20still%20a%20significant%20development%20for%20Harris%20considering%20Trump%20won%20the%20Hawkeye%20State%20in%202020%20by%20eight%20points%20over%20now-President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20have%20to%2