rlotte%20on%20Saturday%20before%20flying%20to%20New%20York%20to%20make%20a%20surprise%20appearance%20on%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night%20Live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20polling%20aggregators%20show%20Trump%20with%20just%20over%20a%20one%20percentage%20point%20lead%20in%20the%20Tar%20Heel%20state.%20Despite%20President%20Obama%20being%20the%20only%20Democratic%20presidential%20hopeful%20to%20carry%20the%20state%20since%202000%2C%20Trump%20only%20narrowly%20held%20off%20President%20Biden%20there%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Harris'%20aides%20mocked%20Trump's%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDonald%20Trump%20is%20worried%20about%20losing%20North%20Carolina%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20spokesperson%20Ammar%20Moussa%20wrote%20on%20X%20under%20two%20siren%20emojis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20Sosnik%2C%20a%20longtime%20advisor%20to%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20a%20North%20Carolina%20native%2C%20doesn't%20see%20Harris'%20path%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20state%20that%20guys%20like%20me%20would%20have%20told%20you%2010%20years%20ago%20would%20be%20a%20Democratic%20state%20now%20like%20Virginia%2C%20but%20it's%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20Carolina%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20level%20playing%20field%26quot%3B%20for%20Democrats%2C%20Sosnik%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20Democrats'%20struggles%20there%20except%20for%20Obama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20competitive.%20It's%20something%20worth%20fighting%20for%2C%20if%20she's%20got%20the%20resources%2C%20she%20should%20stick%20it%20out%2C%20and%20maybe%20she%20could%20win%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sosnik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20campaign%20shot%20back%20that%20it%20was%20Harris%20that%20is%20actually%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20is%20leading%20in%20every%20battleground%20state%20and%20he's%20been%20going%20on%20offense%20in%20historically%20Democrat%20states%20like%20New%20Mexico%20and%20Virginia%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20spokespe