raining%20and%20now%20work%20with%20reputable%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20students%20reach%20Class%207%2C%20the%20alumni%20director%20discusses%20their%20preferred%20high%20schools%20and%20helps%20arrange%20admissions.%20By%20Class%2010%2C%20students%20receive%20career%20counselling%20and%20are%20asked%20to%20select%20their%20top%20three%20colleges%2C%20with%20TCF%20assisting%20in%20securing%20their%20placements.%20The%20foundation%20also%20offers%20personal%20coaching%20in%20subjects%20like%20maths%2C%20science%2C%20economics%2C%20statistics%2C%20business%20studies%2C%20computer%20skills%20and%20English%20to%20support%20students%20after%20school%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20cycle%3A%20Education%20as%20a%20pathway%20out%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20break%20the%20shackles%20of%20poverty.%20A%20house-help%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20profession.%20She%20should%20do%20what%20she%20wants%2C%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20do%20it%20is%20through%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavan%E2%80%99s%20mother%20works%20as%20a%20house-help%2C%20and%20his%20father%20is%20a%20driver.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20person%20in%20his%20family%20to%20even%20complete%20Class%2010.%20%E2%80%9CI%20honestly%20would%20have%20continued%20in%20this%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20if%20it%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20for%20TCF.%20Without%20their%20guidance%2C%20I%20would%20have%20probably%20become%20a%20driver%20like%20my%20father%20after%20Class%2010.%20They%20helped%20me%20in%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%2C%20right%20from%20choosing%20a%20college%20to%20paying%20the%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fup