%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20villages%20have%20their%20schools%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20hamlets%20and%20tribal%20communities%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20concerned%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Padmaja%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20villages%20have%20their%20schools%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20hamlets%20and%20tribal%20communities%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20concerned%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20By%20focusing%20on%20imparting%20hospitality%20skills%20along%20with%20basic%20education%20to%20the%20tribal%20people%20and%20families%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line%2C%20she%20equips%20them%20with%20the%20knowledge%20and%20skills%20to%20become%20stewards%20of%20their%20environment.%20It%20is%20a%20reciprocal%20learning%20experience%2C%20where%20Padmaja%20and%20her%20team%20learn%20from%20the%20ancient%20wisdom%20of%20the%20tribal%20people%2C%20the%20true%20custodians%20of%20the%20land%20for%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurli%20Menon%2C%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EEnvironmentally%20Friendly%20Poetry%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20stayed%20at%20Bhagheera%E2%80%99s%20Camp%20for%20an%20extended%20period%20of%20a%20month%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20only%20an%20ideal%20place%20to%20write%20poetry%20and%20connect%20with%20nature%2C%20but%20also%20inspiring%20to%20see%20a%20camp%20that%20is%20so%20self-sufficient.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20his%20visit%20in%202017%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20regular%20participant%20in%20the%20annual%20reforestation%20work%20at%20the%20camp%2C%20joining%20other%20dedicated%20environmentalists%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20rewild%20Jawai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20of%20community%20engagement%20and%20empowerment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Padmaja%20was%20a%20TEDx%20speaker%20at%20Bodhi%20International%20School%2C%20Jodhpur.%20During%20her%20talk%2C%20she%20shared%20the%20realities%20of%20depleting%20habitats.%20The%20students