-element-caption%5C%22%3EWeLive%E2%80%99s%20residency%20programme%20focuses%20on%20well-being%20and%20work%20readiness%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20WeLive%E2%80%99s%20residency%20programme%20are%20two%20pillars%3A%20well-being%20and%20work%20readiness%20Every%20young%20adult%20who%20joins%20WeLive%E2%80%99s%20aftercare%20residency%20programme%20is%20required%20to%20follow%20a%20structured%20path%20that%20combines%20work%20and%20education.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20resident%20must%20have%20a%20part-time%20job%20and%20be%20enrolled%20in%20a%20study%20course%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ramya.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20those%20who%20have%20passed%20their%2010th%20grade%2C%20we%20prepare%20them%20to%20complete%20their%2012th%20through%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Open%20Schooling%20(NIOS).%20If%20they%E2%80%99ve%20already%20matriculated%2C%20they%20pursue%20higher%20education%20in%20college.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20academic%20and%20professional%20development%20are%20only%20part%20of%20the%20equation.%20Ramya%20emphasises%20that%20these%20young%20adults%20often%20carry%20heavy%20emotional%20burdens.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20have%20endured%20severe%20trauma%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20function%2C%20let%20alone%20focus%20on%20work%20or%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20This%20is%20why%20WeLive%20places%20equal%20importance%20on%20its%20well-being%20pillar%2C%20which%20offers%20counselling%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231083%2Fmental-health-stress-depression-anxiety-covid-19-online-therapy-sessions-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsychological%20support%2C%20and%20mentorshi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231083%2Fmental-health-stress-depression-anxiety-covid-19-online-therapy-sessions-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%3Ep%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20if%20a%20youth